{"title":"选择题","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":15,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2919","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>某同学考试，在N*M的答题卡上写了A,B,C,D四种答案。</p>\n<p>他做完了，又不能交，一看表，离打铃还有N久。</p>\n<p>他开始玩一个游戏：选一个格子X,Y，从这个格子出发向4个方向找相同的选项，找到的再如此。</p>\n<p>求形成的图形的面积。（一个选项占一个单位面积）</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>N M X  Y</p>\n<p>答题卡（矩阵）</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>面积</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3 3 1 2</p>\n<p>A C B</p>\n<p>C C C</p>\n<p>D C A</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>N,M&lt;=15.</p>\n<p>对于33%数据，只有A。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}